-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    <br/>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">我心中的五月天！！！</span></strong>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    <span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    <span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;\">“<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; font-family: 宋体;\">有人说，喜欢一个人，始于颜值，陷于才华，忠于人品。五月天无论什么时候，他们从来没有抱怨过、埋冤过，这是最让我感动的。对于那些贬低他们甚至是抹黑他们，或者对他们音乐造成极大的负面评论时，他们从来也没有生气。五月天只是用心地做每一场演唱会，认真地写好每一首歌，一直努力，一直向前。阿信说过，五月天的歌迷，五月天守护。其实我们丢不掉的不是五月天，而是属于我们青春的满满的回忆与感动。</span></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 26px; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\n    <span style=\"margin: 